# 🌦️ Real-Time Weather Dashboard 🌐

A Streamlit web app that scrapes live weather data for 5 cities using [timeanddate.com](https://www.timeanddate.com/weather/) and plots **temperature** & **humidity** comparisons on a dual-axis bar chart.

## 🔧 Features
- Enter up to 5 cities
- Real-time weather scraping
- Bar chart comparison (Temperature & Humidity)
- Export data as CSV
- Deployed online via Streamlit Cloud

---

## 🚀 How to Run Locally

### 🔗 Prerequisites
Install required packages:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
